HEADWORD: Maladdress
<hw>Mal`ad*dress"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Mal-</ets>
+ <ets>address</ets>.]</ety> <def>Bad address; an awkward, tactless, or
